---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="AMRs — Formic Automate NOW"
  description="Fully managed autonomous mobile robot fleets for pallet and tote movement — dock to staging, line to wrap. No CapEx, 24/7 support, one flat monthly rate, under Formic Full Service."
  ogTitle="Autonomous Mobile Robots — Formic"
  ogDescription="Pallet movement without forklifts. Fully managed AMR fleets under the Formic Full Service model."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/solutions/amrs" slot="head" />

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/solutions">Solutions</a><span class="sep">/</span>AMRs
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">AMRs</div>
    <h1>Pallet movement<br><em>without forklifts.</em></h1>
    <p class="lede">Fully managed AMR fleets that move pallets and totes between zones — dock to staging, line to wrap, finished goods to outbound. No CapEx, one flat monthly rate, and the fleet scales as your flow grows.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/AMR-warehouse.jpg">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · AMR fleet</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">01 — Automate NOW</div>
      <h2>Take the forklift miles <em>off your floor</em>.</h2>
      <p>Forklifts run up the highest single-source injury bill on most CPG and warehousing floors — and they damage pallets, racking, and product along the way. Formic AMRs take over the routine, repeating moves under Full Service, so your drivers focus on inbound and exception work.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Fewer forklift-related injury claims and less product damage</li>
        <li>Predictable cycle times for line-side replenishment</li>
        <li>No CapEx — 24/7 support and 100% maintenance included</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/#cta" class="larr">Get a quote →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/AMR-warehouse.jpg" alt="Formic AMR moving a pallet through a warehouse" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Autonomous · pallet handling</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Talos-0143.jpg" alt="Formic AMR fleet running in a production facility" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Fleet · scaled deployment</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">02 — How It Works</div>
      <h2>Routes that <em>adapt</em>.</h2>
      <p>SLAM-based navigation means no floor tape and no embedded wire — the fleet adapts to pallet placement and floor traffic in real time, and stays synchronized with your WMS and ERP. Start with two AMRs and scale to thirty on the same fleet manager and SLA.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Dynamic routing — adapts to changing floor layouts</li>
        <li>Safe by design — slows and stops around people automatically</li>
        <li>Scales from 2 to 30+ units on the same software and support</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/full-service" class="larr">How Full Service works →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Move pallets<br><em>without moving people.</em></h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="mailto:sales@formic.co" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/solutions" class="btn-ctawh">All Solutions</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
